Description:
    Updates Simlife version, and upgrades generated application

Example:

    simlife upgrade

    Assuming you have Git installed, and you run this command in the Git branch you are using for development, Simlife Upgrader will :
    - checkout a "simlife_upgrade" branch
    - update simlife-bot via npm
    - regenerate your whole application
    - switch back to your development branch, and start the merge
